PN,31201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FA bill to ban so-called 'conversion
OL,8,Ftherapy' has finally been published
OL,9,Fafter eight years of promises by
OL,10,Fsuccessive governments.
OL,12,FThe ban outlaws abusive practices in
OL,13,FEngland and Wales which attempt to
OL,14,Fchange a person's sexuality or gender
OL,15,Fidentity, following almost a decade of
OL,16,Finvestigations by ITV News.
OL,18,FThe draft bill will now be consulted
OL,19,Fon before MPs vote on it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FThe proposed ban sets the criminal
OL,8,Fthreshold for conversion practices as
OL,9,F"conduct that aims to change someone's
OL,10,Fsexual orientation or transgender
OL,11,Fidentity through abusive acts that
OL,12,Fseriously harm the victim".
OL,14,FThe government says forms of abuse
OL,15,Fstill taking place include beatings
OL,16,Fand rape, as well as verbal threats
OL,17,Fand manipulation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FIt has also singled out the religious
OL,8,Fpractices, including exorcism, with
OL,9,FITV News previously exposing intensive
OL,10,Fprayer sessions and religious
OL,11,Ftextbooks aimed at altering someone's
OL,12,Fsexuality.
OL,14,FAs well as criminalising conversion
OL,15,Ftherapy at home, the bill outlaws
OL,16,Fencouraging or assisting people to go
OL,17,Fabroad for similar practices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
