FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FA ban was first promised by Theresa
OL,8,FMay in an interview with ITV News in
OL,9,F2018 ` a pledge repeated by almost all
OL,10,Fof her successors in Number 10.
OL,12,FLabour included a ban on conversion
OL,13,Ftherapy in its manifesto in 2024 and
OL,14,Fis now publishing a bill two years
OL,15,Flater.
OL,17,FAnyone breaking the new law could face
OL,18,Fup to five years in prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FHowever, the ban will face resistance
OL,8,Ffrom concerned groups on several
OL,9,Ffronts.
OL,11,FFirstly, it is a 'trans inclusive ban'
OL,12,Fand covers conversion practices which
OL,13,Ffocus on gender identity.
OL,15,FThe government insists that legitimate
OL,16,Fhealthcare will not be affected and
OL,17,Fthat exploratory conversations with
OL,18,Fmedical professionals or counsellors
OL,19,Fabout gender identity will not be
OL,20,Foutlawed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FBut opponents of a ban worry that the
OL,8,Fbill will have a chilling effect,
OL,9,Fpreventing a doctor or counsellor from
OL,10,Foffering advice and guidance to those
OL,11,Fwho may be confused about their gender
OL,12,Fidentity.
OL,14,FSecondly, while the ban outlaws some
OL,15,Freligious practices, the threshold
OL,16,Fappears to be quite high.
OL,18,FThe government says that it is because
OL,19,Fit wants to protect freedom of belief.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FBut campaigners for a ban argue that
OL,8,Fthe majority of conversion practices
OL,9,Ftake place in religious settings.
OL,11,FTo fall foul of the law, prayer would
OL,12,Fneed to be abusive and cause serious
OL,13,Fharm, for example, by being violent or
OL,14,Fthreatening.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FThe government says religious
OL,8,Fpractices would also meet the
OL,9,Fthreshold if they involved words or
OL,10,Fbehaviour of a sexual nature;
OL,11,Fcontrolling or coercive words or
OL,12,Fbehaviour; use of economic pressure;
OL,13,For use of psychological or emotional
OL,14,Fpressure.
OL,16,FThe government says this mirrors a
OL,17,Fsimilar ban in New Zealand, but some
OL,18,Fcampaigners worry that it excludes
OL,19,Fmore subtle practices, such as private
OL,20,Fone-to-one prayer, where it may be
OL,21,Fdifficult to prove serious harm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FThe debate will likely continue as the
OL,8,Fbill is now consulted upon and
OL,9,Fscrutinised by parliament.
OL,11,FEight years on, there is still no
OL,12,Ftimetable for implementing the ban.
OL,14,FJayne Ozanne, who has campaigned for a
OL,15,Fban for the best part of a decade,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I am delighted and relieved
OL,17,Fthat after eight long years we finally
OL,18,Fhave a draft bill to ban the terrible
OL,19,Fscourge of conversion practices, which
OL,20,Fis far more prevalent in our society
OL,21,Fthan many would choose to believe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,F"It is particularly poignant to me
OL,8,Fthat it comes the day after my
OL,9,Finvestiture for my OBE at Windsor
OL,10,FCastle, where HRH the Prince of Wales
OL,11,Fexpressed his deep concern with me at
OL,12,Fthe fact this was still happening in
OL,13,Fthe UK.
OL,15,F"The devil, as always, is in the
OL,16,Fdetail, and I remain concerned as to
OL,17,Fwhether the ban will fully cover
OL,18,F'praying the gay away' and the thorny
OL,19,Fissue of consent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,F"I myself willingly consented to years
OL,8,Fof prayer by loving friends who were
OL,9,Fkeen 'to help me lead a Godly life' by
OL,10,Ftrying to make me straight.
OL,12,F"The emotional toll of it all nearly
OL,13,Fkilled me. It is particularly damaging
OL,14,Fto young and vulnerable LGBT+ people
OL,15,Fwho want to please their family and
OL,16,Freligious leaders by consenting to
OL,17,Fthese practices."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
