PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FSimon Calvert, deputy director of the
OL,8,FChristian Institute, commented: "After
OL,9,Feight years and five prime ministers,
OL,10,Fis this the best draft they can come
OL,11,Fup with?
OL,13,F"The bill would see parents,
OL,14,Fprofessionals and pastors having to
OL,15,Fanswer to the police for innocent
OL,16,Fconversations that trans activists
OL,17,Fclaim are 'abusive'. It's wide open to
OL,18,Fmisuse."
OL,26,@pD@aOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
