PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782472698
OL,3,CBill finally published to ban
OL,4,C'conversion therapy' in England and
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FHe added: "The government is working
OL,8,Fhand-in-glove with Stonewall on the
OL,9,FBill. But Stonewall has lauded the
OL,10,Flegislation in Victoria, Australia,
OL,11,Fwhere recent guidance from the
OL,12,Fequality commission tells parents to
OL,13,Fask their children which pronouns they
OL,14,Fwant to be called in order to avoid
OL,15,Fbeing accused of conversion therapy.
OL,16,FIt is utter madness."
OL,26,@oD@KOUxD@UO]
